Frederick Burtwell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frederick_Burtwell 0 Augustus Frederick Burtwell (23 December 1894 – 16 November 1948) was an English actor, on stage from 1914, who featured in supporting roles in over 40 British films of the 1930s and 1940s.
